pitt.search.semanticvectors

Class IncrementalTermVectors

  • java.lang.Object
    • pitt.search.semanticvectors.IncrementalTermVectors
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    VectorStore

    public class IncrementalTermVectors
extends Object
implements VectorStore
    Generates term vectors incrementally (i.e. one document at a time) This saves memory compared with other implementations. The training procedure still iterates through all the documents in the Lucene index, so currently this class is purely an optimization, not an implementation of incremental indexing in the sense of being able to add extra terms and documents later after an initial model has been built.
    Author:
    Trevor Cohen, Dominic Widdows
